name: CONTRA CELESTIAL
description:
When the world continues competing to get the magnificent place promised by the previous world, the sun is whacked to always inflames. The promises of eternal glory keep echoing in the serenity of the night, seeming to glow in the light even though the eyes are always closed by the shackled mind. That walls restrain the mind, hatred possessed the lips which make it blackened and freeze. Indeed, the cold and darkness of the shadows come from the heat and the dazzled of blocked sunlight.

2019
Artwork: Vidi Nurhadi Ranadipura
Photographer: Burhan Amaludin
